''' NGC 1275 '''（也稱為英仙座A，[[科德韋爾深空天體表|科德韋爾]]24）是1.5型的[[西佛星系|西佛星系]]<ref name="hoetal1997">{{citation
 | last1 = Ho
 | first1 = Luis C.
 | last2 = Filippenko
 | first2 = Alex V.
 | last3 = Sargent
 | first3 = Wallace L. W.
 | title = A Search for "Dwarf" Seyfert Nuclei. III. Spectroscopic Parameters and Properties of the Host Galaxies
 | year = 1997
 | date = October 1997
 | periodical = Astrophysical Journal Supplement
 | volume = 112
 | pages = 315-390
 | URL = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1997ApJS..112..315H
 | accessdate = 2009-03-31
 | archive-date = 2016-01-10
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110120936/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1997ApJS..112..315H
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>，位在[[英仙座|英仙座]]的方向上，距離大約2億3500萬[[光年|光年]]。NGC 1275對應於[[電波星系|電波星系]]'''英仙座A'''，是位於巨大的[[英仙座星系團|英仙座星系團]]中心的星系。 

== 動力學 ==

[[File:Ngc1275a.jpg|250px]]（HST）的NGC 1275影像。創建者：HST/[[NASA|NASA]]/[[ESA|ESA]]。]]
{{Commonscat|NGC 1275|NGC 1275}}

NGC 1275包含2個星系，在[[英仙座星系團|英仙座星系團]]中央的[[CD星系|CD星系]]，和躺在前方以3,000公里/秒朝向主體高度移動，並且相信應該與[[英仙座星系團|英仙座星系團]]合併的"高速系統"（HVS）<ref>Minkowski R., 1957, in IAU Symp 4, Radio astronomy, p107
</ref>。HVS與[[CD星系|CD星系]]的距離至少有20萬光年，因此不受它的影響<ref>Gillmon K., Sanders J.S., Fabian A.C., [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004MNRAS.348..159G An X-ray absorption analysis of the high-velocity system in NGC 1275] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004MNRAS.348..159G |date=20180808122214 }}, 2004, [[MNRAS|MNRAS]], 348, 159</ref>。星系團中心的星系包含散發出纖維狀[[譜線|譜線]]的大質量網路<ref>Lynds R., [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1970ApJ...159L.151L Improved Photographs of the NGC1275 Phenomenon], 1970, ApJ, 159, L151 
</ref>，看起來似乎會延遲相對論性[[電漿|電漿]]引發的氣泡在中心的[[活躍星系核|活躍星系核]]中的生成<ref>Hatch N.A., Crawford C.S., Johnstone R.M., Fabian A.C.: [http://ukads.nottingham.ac.uk/abs/2006MNRAS.367..433H On the origin and excitation of the extended nebula surrounding NGC1275] {{Wayback|url=http://ukads.nottingham.ac.uk/abs/2006MNRAS.367..433H |date=20080616034456 }}, 2006, [[MNRAS|MNRAS]], 367, 433</ref>。由氣體組成長的氣體絲成螺旋狀的延伸至星系之外，進入數百萬度高溫，充滿了星系團輻射出X射線的氣體。在一條典型螺旋細絲上的氣體包含的質量百萬倍於我們的太陽，但寬度只有200光年，並且可以筆直的延伸達20,000光年<ref>[http://newswise.com/articles/view/543637/ Hubble Sees Magnetic Monster in Erupting Galaxy] {{Wayback|url=http://newswise.com/articles/view/543637/ |date=20111004104743 }} Newswise, Retrieved on [[August_21|August 21]], 2008.</ref>。

細絲的存在引發一個問題，因為它們的溫度比星系團周圍的雲氣低，它們是如何或許維持了一億年之？它們為何不會變暖？消散或是塌縮成為恆星<ref name="nature20080821">{{cite journal | url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v454/n7207/abs/nature07169.html | title=Magnetic support of the optical emission line filaments in NGC 1275 | author=A. C. Fabian, et al. | journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] | volume=454 | pages=968-970 | date=2008-08-21 | access-date=2009-03-31 | archive-date=2009-03-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324064453/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v454/n7207/abs/nature07169.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nytimes20080821">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/26/science/space/26galaxy.html | title=Hubble Images Solve Galactic Filament Mystery | first=Kenneth | last=Chang | publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=2008-08-21 | accessdate=2009-03-31 | archive-date=2011-06-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110601184110/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/26/science/space/26galaxy.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>？一個可能是有著微弱的磁場（大約地球磁場強度的萬分之一）施加了足夠的力量使[[離子|離子]]在螺線上聚集<ref name="nature20080821"/><ref name="nytimes20080821"/>。

NGC 1275 含有130億太陽質量的分子雲。<ref name=Lim2008>
{{cite journal
| volume = 672
| pages = 252–265
| last1 = Lim
